sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant DB

    Admin->>Frontend: Enter email & password
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/users/login
    Backend->>DB: Find user by email
    DB-->>Backend: User (includes isAdmin)
    alt Not admin or invalid credentials
        Backend-->>Frontend: 401/403 error
        Frontend-->>Admin: Show error
    else Admin verified
        Backend-->>Frontend: 200 OK (JWT token)
        Frontend-->>Admin: Redirect to Admin Dashboard
    end
